title: BRICKELL 2BED / 2BATH // FURNISHED
posting_body: ['Wonderful 2 bed / 2 bath home with amazing 15th floor city views!', ' Over 1100 sq/ft.  Available immediately ($4500/mo if rented unfurnished).', ' Features super rare European Oak wood floors (never ever see this here - creates a really beautiful look and feel), stainless steel appliances, granite counter tops, floor to ceiling impact windows, private balcony w/ glass railings, slide out kitchen pantry drawers, ample master bathroom storage space, walk-in closets in both bedrooms & a washer/dryer in unit.', ' One parking space.', 'Resort style amenities include: Fitness center, 2 infinity edged pools, steam rooms, theatre room, club room, party room, pool table & lounge.', '24 hour concierge & valet parking.', "Located in coveted downtown Brickell, walking distance to Brickell City Center, Mary Brickell Village & right in the heart of Miami's finest dining, shopping & night life!", 'Call me for the best looking rentals in Brickell, Edgewater and Midtown.', 'Christopher Smyk -', 'show contact info', 'or hit reply above', 'Axis Realty Trust', 'Miami FL']
